==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ingeminate
<hw>In*gem"i*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Ingeminated</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Ingeminating</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L.
<ets>ingeminatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>ingeminare</ets> to double; pref.
