[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q> . . . She yet <qex>ingeminates</qex>⟦br⟧
The last of sounds, and what she hears relates.</q>
<rj><qau>Sandys.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ingemination</ent>⟦br⟧
